headline: Property & Casualty Insurance Stocks Q2 Teardown: Erie Indemnity (NASDAQ:ERIE) Vs The Rest
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how property & casualty insurance stocks fared in Q2, starting with Erie Indemnity (NASDAQ:ERIE).
